dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Taylor County, WI 2014
dc_description_s: This data layer represents hydrography for Taylor County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase “Taylor_Hydro_2014.gdb”. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are “Taylor_HydroLine_2014” and “Taylor_HydroPoly_2014'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
